{"tid":369502,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有時拍拖拍到咁不如算數","createTime":"2017-08-22T11:21:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T02:44:34.000Z","uid":58547,"like":618,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ec336df0ef3090b9369a46fa34be1f60f806abd","tid":369502,"uid":58547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:21:16.000Z","msg":"我唔知都應唔應該咁計住計住 但真係好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n平時出街等佢一頭半個鐘已經係閒事 d時間係多到我可以去佢屋企接佢<br />\n<br />\n小小事就話要分手 上之唔小心咬到佢咀唇 分手 唔小心滴左滴汁落隻舊鞋度 分手<br />\n<br />\n成日十問九唔應 問佢聽日睇唔睇戲問左 4 5 次先覆 今日佢話去做gym唔講幾點完 我有既info就係<br />\n1. 我去左gym<br />\n2. 同個coach傾左1個鐘<br />\n3. Gym地址<br />\n我係度已經等左差唔多半個幾鐘 冇覆過我 我真係唔知點 走又唔係 繼續等又唔知要等到幾耐<br />\n<br />\n成日講野講頭唔講尾 然後話大家唔夾要分手 <br />\n<br />\n好啦呻下啫 繼續等"},{"pid":"96dd15423e00e26f3e2d8c20ef476f79be4c7df7","tid":369502,"uid":35501,"like":441,"dislike":3,"score":438,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:22:13.000Z","msg":"多謝樓主犧牲自己"},{"pid":"f093c8bfdc3469fd826cbcf3756195fc81166130","tid":369502,"uid":130513,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:23:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"87f222e9294493ef7d2be2557be7d82bc5559752","tid":369502,"uid":117263,"like":162,"dislike":0,"score":162,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:24:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">放條港女出嚟遺害其他人</span></span>"},{"pid":"b32e1e1615edd3d85d49c87909033915f49a44d7","tid":369502,"uid":116609,"like":84,"dislike":0,"score":84,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:24:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">通常咁都帽事嘅</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191ff90a81a69f744cba6d2f656adcb5688a60a5","tid":369502,"uid":58547,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:26:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝樓主犧牲自己</blockquote><br />\n唔駛客氣 同我傾下計好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee11384eb4fbc89506e34e15b892696d091ee925","tid":369502,"uid":6958,"like":44,"dislike":2,"sco