"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T15:48:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我唔知都應唔應該咁計住計住 但真係好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n平時出街等佢一頭半個鐘已經係閒事 d時間係多到我可以去佢屋企接佢<br />\n<br />\n小小事就話要分手 上之唔小心咬到佢咀唇 分手 唔小心滴左滴汁落隻舊鞋度 分手<br />\n<br />\n成日十問九唔應 問佢聽日睇唔睇戲問左 4 5 次先覆 今日佢話去做gym唔講幾點完 我有既info就係<br />\n1. 我去左gym<br />\n2. 同個coach傾左1個鐘<br />\n3. Gym地址<br />\n我係度已經等左差唔多半個幾鐘 冇覆過我 我真係唔知點 走又唔係 繼續等又唔知要等到幾耐<br />\n<br />\n成日講野講頭唔講尾 然後話大家唔夾要分手 <br />\n<br />\n好啦呻下啫 繼續等</blockquote><br />\n小小事都嗌分手 拍黎為咩 下個更可愛呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8348f88d3d1e5779507a90638408edec0828aa9e","tid":369502,"uid":3646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T15:51:06.000Z","msg":"咁既款似帽前景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a14e168d5f88fb6288d61eaf67a2af99d1d3e3c","tid":369502,"uid":16041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T16:06:41.000Z","msg":"Gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n男人老狗先做gym"},{"pid":"9f6d0aff4adbf2d14e3a8d102e2159df12255a1a","tid":369502,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T16:08:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n男人老狗先做gym</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7827f1a8912718b1ae97919393707bd94fd17c7","tid":369502,"uid":6796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T16:13:52.000Z","msg":"姐係佢唔鐘意你囉其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好怪我直 但樓主唔好哂時間啦真係<br />\n你搵過好d既仲好啦"},{"pid":"783a5eb08c99201570e4722182cd55e154a50594","tid":369502,"uid":136645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T16:44:34.000Z","msg":"鳩痕咪叫雞囉，洗乜為左屌西，買女人怕"},{"pid":"9a1ea65141134c44b57b521913066fce083a64e7","tid":369502,"uid":529,"